  • Konstruktordetails

    • Caregiver

      public Caregiver(String username, String firstName, String surname, LocalDate dateOfBirth, String telephoneNumber, String password, boolean isAdmin, boolean locked, String lockedDate)
      This constructor creates a new Caregiver with the given properties. The password is hashed before it is stored.
      Parameter:
      username - The username of the Caregiver.
      firstName - The first name of the Caregiver.
      surname - The surname of the Caregiver.
      dateOfBirth - The date of birth of the Caregiver.
      telephoneNumber - The telephone number of the Caregiver.
      password - The password of the Caregiver.
      isAdmin - A flag indicating whether the Caregiver is an admin.
      locked - A flag indicating whether the Caregiver is locked.
      lockedDate - The date when the Caregiver was locked.

    • Caregiver

      public Caregiver(long pid, String username, String firstName, String surname, LocalDate dateOfBirth, String telephoneNumber, String password_hash, boolean isAdmin)
      This constructor creates a new Caregiver with the given properties. The password is assumed to be already hashed.
      Parameter:
      pid - The unique identifier for the Caregiver.
      username - The username of the Caregiver.
      firstName - The first name of the Caregiver.
      surname - The surname of the Caregiver.
      dateOfBirth - The date of birth of the Caregiver.
      telephoneNumber - The telephone number of the Caregiver.
      password_hash - The hashed password of the Caregiver.
      isAdmin - A flag indicating whether the Caregiver is an admin.
